<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA99">
<l>ceppēn tiḷamulaiyāṭ kāṇavō tīppaṭukāṭ</l>
<l>ṭappēyk kaṇamavaitāṅ kāṇavō - ceppeṉakkoṉ</l>
<l>ṟākattā ṉaṅkān taṉalumiḻu maivāya</l>
<l>nākattā yāṭu ṉaṭam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it for her with pot[-like] eminent young breasts to see, or is it the assembly</l>
<l>of gaṇas [and] demonesses in the burning cremation ground to see, tell me for once</l>
 <l>– your dance danced as one with five-mouthed snakes</l>
<l>that open [their] mouths [and] spit fire?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
